= 阅读 (Reading) - 25 minutes

== Section 2: 长篇阅读

*文章：*

互联网改变了我们的生活方式。人们可以通过网络购物、工作、学习和交朋友。但是，过度使用互联网也会带来一些问题，比如影响视力、浪费时间和减少面对面的交流。因此，我们应该合理使用互联网。

+ How has the internet changed our lives?
  - A) Made life worse 
  - B) Enabled shopping, work, learning, friendship ✓ 
  - C) Destroyed society

+ What are the problems mentioned about excessive internet use?
  - A) Only eye problems 
  - B) Eye problems, wasting time, less face-to-face interaction ✓ 
  - C) No problems

+ What does the author suggest?
  - A) Don't use internet 
  - B) Use it moderately ✓ 
  - C) Use it all the time

